<br>
PoP has really hurt the pure melee classes as a whole and has really highlighted the weaknesses of the classes.  As it stands, monks need a little loving to come back into line with the pure melees and the melees as a whole need to be brought up in line with the casters.  I know of too many warriors and monks that have quit and moved on to other toons or left EQ altogether.  Sadly, its the better players that I see leaving.<br>
<br>
